{"tid":471130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[炮彈] 唧車當凳坐 工人彈起撞電梯門夾腳 Angry Bird","createTime":"2017-11-17T03:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T20:31:50.000Z","uid":17103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"972610da6c6cf9c67f058bc7908ad4f33a6b6329","tid":471130,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:32:41.000Z","msg":"沙田火炭坳背灣街一幢工業大廈，昨日發生罕見意外。一名工人坐在唧車上乘搭升降機，期間唧車撞向升降機鐵閘，令工人彈起，一同拍向鐵閘夾住雙腳，工人慌忙按警鐘求救，最終由消防員救出送院。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171117/large/1510880616_fa88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171117%2Flarge%2F1510880616_fa88.jpg&h=3de55a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工人坐在唧車上，期間唧車溜前，令他撞落升降機鐵閘。(閉路電視畫面)<br />\n<br />\n意外經過被現場閉路電視攝下，並在網上流傳。片中可見，事發於昨日下午3時17分，一名年約50歲的工人，推唧車搭乘升降機。升降機是工廈舊款，要人手拉上門和鐵閘。當升降機上升之際，該工人坐在唧車上，並背靠手柄往後伸展。升至6樓位置，唧車撞向升降機鐵閘，整部唧車登時垂直，令工人連人帶唧車猛力拍落鐵閘，雙腳被夾在唧車與鐵閘之間，動彈不得，升降機即時停止運作；只見工人狀甚狼狽，按動緊急掣求救。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171117/large/1510884500_249a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171117%2Flarge%2F1510884500_249a.jpg&h=0f0b5d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事的唧車仍然停放在升降機內。(張培生攝)<br />\n<br />\n在場目擊者形容，工人將唧車當按摩椅，疑背靠唧車時令它鬆手掣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171117/large/1510884503_b71e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171117%2Flarge%2F1510884503_b71e.jpg&h=1edafb0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n升降機暫停使用，可見鐵閘被撞毀的痕迹。(張培生攝)<br />\n<br />\n消防處於3時26分接獲有人困電梯的報告，到場後將他救出，送威爾斯醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171117/large/1510884506_2ed7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171117%2Flarge%2F1510884506_2ed7.jpg&h=e96c33cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事升降機停用，其他工人使用其他升降機。(張培生攝)<br />\n<br />\n記者今早到現場工廈了解，涉事升降機為8號載貨升降機，現時停在6樓，掛上「暫停使用」的圍欄，出事的唧車仍然停放在升降機內，可見是一部電動唧車。而救援用的鋁梯和敷料包裝則散滿地上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171117/large/1510880617_1771.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171117%2Flarge%2F1510880617_1771.jpg&h=c50a6980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工人坐在唧車上，背靠手柄往後伸。(閉路電視畫面)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171117/large/1510880618_ed47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171117%2Flarge%2F1510880618_ed47.jpg&h=87dc1a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唧車突然溜前。(閉路電視畫面)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171117/large/1510880619_ed2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171117%2Flarge%2F1510880619_ed2a.jpg&h=ba194054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工人按動緊急掣求救。(閉路電視畫面)"},{"pid":"72bf018111b2aa92fb18ccbf86a92558b1cbb482","tid":471130,"uid":2247,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"sorry 笑左"},{"pid":"d08c42f3c40b98d8703782b84ee608d45421f770","tid":471130,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:38:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sorry 笑左</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a78ccff2c55414585e3489eb91a009bda5c3dff7","tid":471130,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dce5f2acdce3fd837fbcccb9c43b62e1ccd74d7","tid":471130,"uid":57382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:41:30.000Z","msg":"賠錢都賠死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef79580943b5844bcf08f2090a45f943df406c32","tid":471130,"uid":37751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedB